<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<e:Skin class="GameSkin" width="640" height="1136" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">

	<e:Image source="plus" x="313" y="83"/>
</e:Skin>

<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<e:Skin class="LoadingSkin" width="640" height="960" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">
	<e:Rect id="bg" left="0" right="0" top="0" bottom="0" fillColor="0x110d0d"/>
	<e:Image id="logo" source="ws_logo" y="193" horizontalCenter="0"/>
	<e:Group height="21" width="500" horizontalCenter="0" verticalCenter="20.5" visible="false">
		<e:Image id="loadingBar" source="ws_loading_bar" scale9Grid="11,2,311,17" left="0" right="0" top="0" bottom="0"/>
		<e:Image id="loadings" source="ws_loadings" scale9Grid="7,2,318,17" top="0" bottom="0" left="0" width="500"/>
	</e:Group>
	<e:Image id="logos" source="ws_logos" y="714" horizontalCenter="0"/>
</e:Skin>

<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<e:Skin class="StartSkin" width="640" height="1136" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">
	<e:Image id="btnStart" y="604" horizontalCenter="0.5" source="button_start"/>
	<e:Image source="button_start" x="129" y="327"/>
	<e:Image source="word2" y="645" horizontalCenter="0"/>
</e:Skin>

<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<e:Skin class="UploadSkin" width="640" height="960" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">
	<e:Rect right="0" bottom="0" left="0" top="0" fillAlpha="0.36" x="10" y="10"/>
	<e:Group id="mainLayer" left="0" right="0" top="0" bottom="0">
		<e:Image id="bg" scale9Grid="34,34,409,604" horizontalCenter="0.5" verticalCenter="0.5" height="341" width="585" source="ws_upload_bg"/>
		<e:Label id="tipLabel" width="498" size="35" horizontalCenter="0" textColor="0x636364" height="72" verticalAlign="middle" text="网络错误" textAlign="center" fontFamily="微软雅黑" y="451"/>
		<e:Image id="btnRetry" scale9Grid="28,4,303,52" width="486" y="563" source="ws_upload_btn" height="74" horizontalCenter="0"/>
		<e:Label id="labelBtn" text="重   试" y="585" bold="true" touchEnabled="false" horizontalCenter="0.5" fontFamily="微软雅黑"/>
		<e:Label id="btnClose" text="X" x="559" y="333" textColor="0x66CD33" size="50" fontFamily="微软雅黑"/>
		<e:Label id="title" text="加载失败" y="332" textColor="0x66CD33" fontFamily="微软雅黑" size="50" bold="true" horizontalCenter="0"/>
	</e:Group>
	<e:Image id="loading" source="ws_upload_loading" anchorOffsetX="55" anchorOffsetY="55" horizontalCenter="0" verticalCenter="0"/>
</e:Skin>
